including a jacket that plays music in the

00:03:46.870 --> 00:03:52.300
hood using bluetooth connected to your smart
phone and a new virtual reality jacket. The

00:03:52.300 --> 00:03:57.130
Out of Body Experience jacket is embedded
with sensors that allow the movement of your

00:03:57.130 --> 00:04:03.230
body to effect VR. Turning the user into an
immersive controller by wearing a normal-looking

00:04:03.230 --> 00:04:05.580
